Deccan Al

Assignment Workflow Write-up

Approach

This workflow implements an Al-

powered recruiting pipeline that takes a job description as input and returns a ranked list of interested, qualified candidates. The system combines LLM-based agents with structured data (Google Sheets) and presents results via an interactive dashboard.

Core Philosophy: Automate the top- of-funnel candidate sourcing and interest qualification using Al agents, while keeping human oversight

